ak of works and faith? James 2: 20-</div><div class="t m765 x3f h4 y13c2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">22. </div><div class="t m1d2 x4e h4 y934 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t mae9 x5b h4 y934 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How is faith said to work? Gal. 5: 6. </div><div class="t m1d5 x28 h4 y12fd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m794 x5b h4 y12fd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Of what is faith a fruit? Gal. 5: 22. </div><div class="t m127 x28 h4 y1d2e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m1868 x5b h4 y1d2e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is the ultimate purpose of faith? 1 Peter 1: 8, 9. </div><div class="t mfc5 x64 h4 yead ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14). How may victory over the world be obtained? 1 John 5: 4. </div><div class="t me4 x64 h4 y118e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t m1b93 x5b h4 y118d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How are salvation and faith spoken of? Eph. 2: 8. </div><div class="t m490 x3f h4 yf4a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Note 2. </div><div class="t me4 x64 h4 y1f7d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m173e x5b h4 y11b5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Relate an instance of saving faith. John 5: 1-9. Note 3. </div><div class="t me4 x64 h4 y1117 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m11c0 x5b h4 y1117 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What spiritual lesson may be learned from this? Note 4. </div><div class="t me4 x64 h4 y1193 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14. </div><div class="t m19d7 x5b h4 y108f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Repeat the precious promise in Mark 11: 24. Note 5. </div><div class="t me4 x64 h4 yb89 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">15. </div><div class="t m53b x5b h4 yb89 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In what prayer may all join? Mark 9: 24. </div><div class="t me4 x64 h4 y1ec6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16. </div><div class="t mf65 x5b h4 y1ec6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In what blessed prayer may we be included? Luke 22: 32. </div><div class="t m492 x9a h4 y101e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Notes </div><div class="t m1437 x66